  "texts": [
    "The activities must be consistent with the contractual agreements and usage conditions to enable self-determination.",
    "Accordingly, the data asset itself in Fig. 1 is not directly linked to the data provider or consumer (Nagel & Lycklama, 2021).",
    "Instead, the data provider and data consumer perform value chain activities on the data asset.",
    "The data infrastructure component enforces terms and conditions determined in the contractual agreement (Munoz-Arcentales et al., 2019; Nagel & Lycklama, 2021).",
    "It is centrally located in the model since it works between the data provider and consumer by validating and executing terms and restrictions (Nagel & Lycklama, 2021), specified in the contractual agreement (see Fig. 1)."
  ],
